window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Probing into the new world of BDSM and coming to grips with her new-found sensuality, we left Brooklyn at a crossroads in her love life.</p> <p>Her sex-ploration into this gratifying, new world meant leaving her fears behind, and letting go of the notion that she is a “good girl” who plays by the rules of a religious, conservative upbringing. Now free from shame, Brooklyn is no longer bound by familial and societal dynamics, determined to experience life joy free of the guilt she carried for so long. <br> <br> In this highly anticipated sequel to <i>Brooklyn Unbound</i>, Brooklyn finds herself unleashed, navigating kinky new waters on a mission of self-discovery and enjoying pleasures she once thought were unattainable. However, in succumbing to her carnal desires, she not only entraps herself in a love triangle with J and a new suitor, but also struggles to find balance between the delicious adventures of her new life and the responsibilities she has to her loved ones and career.<br> <br> As Brooklyn continues to indulge in the limitless possibilities and challenges that living unbound yields, she invites more drama into her life than even she could’ve anticipated. Coming into her own comes with a price, and she wonders if this life is worth the possibility of losing the people she loves in her quest of being truly, sexually free.</p>"; 
